<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Harwill says still in talks.</title>
<headline>Harwill says still in talks.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harwill Investments Ltd said on Monday it was still involved in talks which could have an impact on its share price and urged shareholders to exercise caution in their dealings.</p>
<p>It gave no further details in a brief announcement.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
